==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sufficiently
<hw>Suf*fi"cient*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>To a sufficient degree;
to a degree that answers the purpose, or gives content; enough; <as>as,
we are <ex>sufficiently</ex> supplied with food; a man
<ex>sufficiently</ex> qualified for the discharge of his official
duties</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sufficing</ent>⟦br⟧
